    // Mixed/Code-switching
    "Dr. 田中 presented her research at MIT's AI conference.",
    // Transliteration variants
    "Москва (Moskva/Moscow) hosted the 東京 (Tokyo) delegation.",
    // Names with diacritics
    "François Müller and José García met in São Paulo.",
    // Single-name entities
    "Pelé, Madonna, and Cher performed at the concert.",
    // Honorifics
    "Her Majesty Queen Elizabeth II met Prime Minister शर्मा.",
